elements.2211.03024_8e6ee980f97875832481d2ef144d7: Recent increases in computing power have enabled the numerical simulation of many complex flow problems that are of practical and strategic interest for naval applications
elements.2211.03024_fa2a0b31ed8d8e562a9f4a58827e8: A noticeable area of advancement is the computation of turbulent, two-phase flows resulting from wave breaking and other multiphase flow processes such as cavitation that can generate underwater sound and entrain bubbles in ship wakes, among other effects
elements.2211.03024_bd81cf761528d653f19d37560cc0f: Although advanced flow solvers are sophisticated and are capable of simulating high Reynolds number flows on large numbers of grid points, challenges in data analysis remain
elements.2211.03024_cf0719d11592cc3c7e03f68340168: Specifically, there is a critical need to transform highly resolved flow fields described on fine grids at discrete time steps into physically resolved features for which the flow dynamics can be understood and utilized in naval applications
elements.2211.03024_2750d20ade7b942d03b7fa1ab43ac: This paper presents our recent efforts in this field
elements.2211.03024_ea558c14762fdab3300417d5594b8: In previous works, we developed a novel algorithm to track bubbles in breaking wave simulations and to interpret their dynamical behavior over time
elements.2211.03024_57da10a42a2bf474ef03aea293807: We also discovered a new physical mechanism driving bubble production within breaking wave crests
elements.2211.03024_4c661aadf482a55d8a9fa92b21e1b: 2021b) and developed a model to relate bubble behaviors to underwater sound generation
elements.2211.03024_87ee225485c7d8a63286102a6eca7: In this work, we applied our bubble tracking algorithm to the breaking waves simulations and investigated the bubble trajectories, bubble creation mechanisms, and bubble acoustics based on our previous works.
elements.2211.03024_9acbe503857e61c56336907db1fc4: Bubbles play critical roles in ocean
elements.2211.03024_e72965270d0ea4389fc98cec5da4b: atmosphere processes and naval applications, such as ship hydrodynamics
elements.2211.03024_ba5539508f39fabd7bd8583cf6934: Specifically, it is important to understand the creation mechanisms, transport behaviors, and acoustic properties of bubbles because they can affect the drag on ship hulls and ships' acoustic and optical signatures
elements.2211.03024_16757fb678f34b7291ed17315682a: Consequently, numerous experimental and numerical studies have been conducted on the bubbles in breaking waves and their applications to ship hydrodynamics
elements.2211.03024_7fe2514c4b7a45b34c52724181564: (2021) investigated the bubble size spectrum in breaking waves or free-surface turbulence and demonstrated that super-Hinze-scale bubbles (bubbles whose radii exceed the Hinze scale) follow a
elements.2211.03024_a3f3dc50d70b4b284b010ba61d728: Super-Hinze-scale bubbles are created by a fragmentation cascade process
elements.2211.03024_d491876c4679b042b049a6e8f434f: 2000), where large bubbles break up into smaller bubbles due to turbulent fluctuations
elements.2211.03024_300d09047cceb8ae1c193ac7b1fc1: (2016) investigated bubble distributions with regard to ship hydrodynamics
elements.2211.03024_088d67e59202a5d6b5b768447a777: The above works have advanced our understanding of the physics of bubbly flows in the context of breaking waves and ship hydrodynamics
elements.2211.03024_72d5e3ffd20c50d363b64a59f1f2f: However, some challenges remain in this field
elements.2211.03024_368653d6bfda0adde4f88941ca0e1: For example, these works studied the statistics of bubbles at only single instances in time because of the limitation of the conventional bubble identification algorithm, which cannot track bubbles temporally and thus cannot detect their evolutionary behavior over time
elements.2211.03024_a97e14ad90d42a483fda21e3e0893: Therefore, the fragmentation, coalescence, and trajectories of bubbles were not captured in previous studies
elements.2211.03024_5ca85e4f0c8859b556dd81da007f2: Recently, we developed a novel algorithm (Gao et al.,
elements.2211.03024_d0376ff6261951ed52e4487439d0d: 2021a) to track bubbles and detect their evolutionary behaviors over time by making connections among bubbles between sequential time instances
elements.2211.03024_ff0262488980bdd16649391208278: Specifically, our algorithm classifies bubble behaviors into five categories
elements.2211.03024_05a6c42da333f3fe7e167d857291a: Based on these bubble behaviors, the algorithm derives constraints on the bubble volumes, velocities, and positions at two sequential time instances and then tries to make connections among the bubbles at these successive instances in time by selecting the minimum value within a network of error functions defined by these constraints
elements.2211.03024_dbceebbbe733f3fa49074c957f931: By following the networks among bubbles over time, this algorithm is capable of temporally tracking bubbles to obtain their trajectories
elements.2211.03024_2eea2d3aef67dcd89734fb07adcec: Moreover, the algorithm can be used to identify newly formed bubbles when they are not associated with any bubbles at the previous time step
elements.2211.03024_ff79c313e1fcb95e79b690291225d: The algorithm here is limited to binary fragmentation and binary coalescence events
elements.2211.03024_05d89ea83ade30fc3f743466b73d3: In other words, the algorithm cannot detect the event that a bubble breaks up into three and more
elements.2211.03024_03c2abfb9c2189788806face012cd: (multiple fragmentation) or the event that three or more bubbles merge into one
elements.2211.03024_8451344d63ff689c98ed2e3189a1d: This is because establishing network becomes much complex when considering multiple fragmentation and coalescence
elements.2211.03024_770d88a7bf188266d02558ea1f6ec: To ascertain the mechanism responsible for creating bubbles, previous studies have focused primarily on the bubble fragmentation cascade process
elements.2211.03024_e39aeaadf028e85ad104150939c6e: During the bubble fragmentation cascade process, large bubbles are fragmented into smaller ones due to turbulent fluctuation
elements.2211.03024_4c4fe498ba3936f7d8ad22446c94c: (2021b) studied the bubble generation dynamics in a breaking wave
elements.2211.03024_f4b450c43dd7d2eeeb5de80a594be: In their work, they identified a bubble formation mechanism called air cylinder instability and provided a formula expressing its theoretical dispersion
elements.2211.03024_256eeb71e05311414c5f6736aaacc: Different from the fragmentation cascade process, the cylinder instability produces bubbles through an interface instability
elements.2211.03024_97d4d3a0a870db36d25dd6b0fd012: They compared simulation results with the theory and found good agreement
elements.2211.03024_34a37285d19b12104402f6026e979: However, some questions regarding the bubble creation mechanism remain
elements.2211.03024_6feb00d2a30927ca7dc1347092b32: For example, how many air cylinders are created in a breaking wave, and how many bubbles are created when an air cylinder breakup? Furthermore, how important is the cylinder instability mechanism to the overall formation of bubbles? In the present work, we examine the wave breaking process, bubble creation events, and the bubble size spectrum to quantify the importance of the air cylinder instability to the production of bubbles to some extent

elements.2211.03024_de30558cd14d66ba66ec95446d2f4: In this work, we adopted a novel algorithm to track bubbles and detect their evolutionary behaviors over time during breaking wave simulations and investigated various bubble creation mechanisms and bubble trajectories
elements.2211.03024_fa0163773364866d0d94283988ae8: The results show that instability along the boundary of an air cylinder is an important mechanism for bubble creation and has significant effects on the initial breaking wave process and bubble size spectrum
elements.2211.03024_56bbe7fc5b28105e0c794e16f7d9a: Bubble trajectories show three unique patterns in breaking waves
elements.2211.03024_b2f42c4c6e12a8db4719b537239ee: Specifically, we observed trajectories with rotational motion, trajectories pointing forward and upward, and parallel trajectories
elements.2211.03024_bc47e39e92a7f350b2fd7fb4c01d0: Finally, we investigated the acoustics of newly formed bubbles and calculated the noise spectrogram radiated by a breaking wave
elements.2211.03024_d1cdd629414de00742b272d2b3999: In future work, we will conduct more detailed studies on bubble creation mechanisms, bubble trajectories interacting with breaking wave flow fields, and wave noise.
